  "description": "Unique lego-like bricks resource pack for Minecraft! Immerse yourself in a vibrant colorful world full of plastic bricks! Start building your Brickcraft masterpiece now!",
  "body": "<H6 id=\"top\"></H6>\n\n<center>\n\t<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/uBhFaBG\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/709027134441652325?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&label=Discord&labelColor=ffffff&color=5865f2&link=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FuBhFaBG\" style=\"height: 50px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a>\n\t<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://patreon.com/alextestria\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3Dalextestria%26type%3Dpatrons&style=for-the-badge&logoColor=0d0d0d&labelColor=ffffff&color=f7404b&link=https%3A%2F%2Fpatreon.com%2Falextestria\" style=\"height: 50px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a>\n\t<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/brickcraft\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/535052?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&label=Curseforge&labelColor=ffffff&color=f16436&link=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curseforge.com%2Fminecraft%2Ftexture-packs%2Fbrickcraft\" style=\"height: 50px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a>\n\t<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/brickcraft\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/OXnVT7vC?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth&labelColor=ffffff&color=1bd96a&link=https%3A%2F%2Fmodrinth.com%2Fresourcepack%2Fbrickcraft\" style=\"height: 50px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a>\n\t<br>\n\t<br>\n</center>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Brickcraft-by-AlexTestria-1024x-WEBP.webp\" alt=\"Brickcraft by Alex Testria\" width=\"850\" height=\"200\">\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n---\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n<center>\n<font size=10 color=\"ffffff\"><b>Hello, 👋🏻 I'm AlexTestria</b></font><br>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<font size=4>\nI’m a self-taught 3D artist/game designer.\nVery excited to learn UI/UX- and illustration design. <br>\nSince November 2022 I am fighting against <b>very aggressive sarcoma cancer.</b><br>\nThanks to my Patrons for funding my treatments! 🤍\n</font>\n</center>\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n---\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://patreon.com/alextestria\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Support-Me-On-Patreon-png.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a> <a href=\"https://brickcraft.de\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Brickcraft-Official-Website.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uBhFaBG\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Join-Our-Discord.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a> <br>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://brickcraft.de\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Full-Download-Black.webp\" width=\"850\" height=\"200\"></a> \n&nbsp;\n\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/VcH0MuhWa8U\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/rK21JiVb1z8\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n<center>\n<font size=10 color=\"ffffff\"><b>FAQ</b></font><br>\n</center>\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary>Do I need shaders or any mods?</summary>\nNo, you do _not_ need shaders or mods to use Brickcraft.<br> It was conceptualized as the only legolike brick pack for 100% Vanilla Minecraft. <br> Premium Edition and Extreme Edition however are specially made with shaders in mind.\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Can I play Brickcraft on Bedrock or Pocket Edition?</summary>\nNo, sadly Bedrock and Pocket Edition are missing key 3D modelling features to implement 3D blocks.\n<br>Due to this limitation it is not possible to make Brickcraft functional on these editions or console.\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>How do I install resource packs?</summary>\nIt’s you first time installing a resource pack? This is the <a href=\"https://brickcraft.de/instructions\" target=\"_blank\">perfect guide</a> you’ll ever need! <br>It is much more simple to set everything up than you might think.\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>The resource pack is lagging!</summary>\nBecause Brickcraft only uses 3D Models to achieve its look, it can lag quite a lot at medium to higher render distances. Try setting your render distance between two and six chunks.<br>\n<a href=\"https://brickcraft.de/instructions\" target=\"_blank\">Check out this page for additional tips!</a>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Why does the resource pack cost money?</summary>\nSince November 2022 I am fighting against an extremely aggressive sarcoma cancer at 22 years old.<br>\nMost of my profit goes directly towards my treatments and rent. <br>\nWithout charging money, I wouldn't be able to further develop Brickcraft or even continue to live my life.\n</details>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n\n<center>\n<iframe src=\"https://discord.com/widget?id=709027134441652325&theme=dark\" width=\"350\" height=\"500\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts\"></iframe>\n</iframe>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/uBhFaBG\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Join-Our-Discord.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/brickcraft\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/Follow-On-CurseForge.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/brickcraft-lego-like-bricks-ultrarealistic-in-minecraft/\"><img src=\"https://brickcraft.de/wp-content/uploads/PlanetMinecraft.webp\" width=\"275\" height=\"65\"></a>\n</center>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n---\n\n\n```\nBrickcraft is not in any way affiliated with LEGO®.\nLEGO® is a trademark of the LEGO Group of companies which does not sponsor, authorize, or endorse this resource pack.\n```\n```\nNot approved by or associated with Mojang or Microsoft.\n```",
